flowchart TD
    A[Error Raised] --> B[Lookup AppError.Code]
    B --> C[Resolve i18n Key]
    C --> D{Locale Available?}
    D -- No --> E[Fallback to en-US]
    D -- Yes --> F[Render Title + Body]
    E --> F
    F --> G[Apply Copy Format Template]
    G --> H[Inject Variables]
    H --> I[Display in Modal]
